# QR Code Generator (Python)

This is a simple Python script that generates a QR code from user input (text or URL) and saves it as a `.png` image.

---

## ðŸ“Œ Features

- Accepts any text or URL as input
- Generates a high-quality QR code
- Saves the QR code as an image file (`your_qrcode.png`)
- Custom colors (green on white)

